  <brief_title>Multicentric Randomised Trial for Resectable Gastric Cancer</brief_title>
  <acronym>CRITICS-II</acronym>
  <official_title>A Multicentre Randomised Phase II Trial of Neo-adjuvant Chemotherapy Followed by Surgery vs. Neo-adjuvant Chemotherapy and Subsequent Chemoradiotherapy Followed by Surgery vs. Neo-adjuvant Chemoradiotherapy Followed by Surgery in Resectable Gastric Cancer</official_title>
